songs.title: Decaydance
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Close your eyes
Dream alone
When you arise
You will be home

[Chorus]
Close your eyes
Dream alone
When you arise
You will be home


[Verse 2]
Take a chance at something comin' in
Everyone will win

Take a chance at something comin' in
Everyone is already away
(I can't think straight)
Take a chance at something comin' in
Everyone will win
(I feel like we can win)

[Chorus]
Close your eyes
Dream alone
When you arise
You will be home
Close your eyes
Dream alone
When you arise
You will be home

[Conclusion]
Take a chance at something comin' in
Everyone is already away
(I feel like I can't think straight)
Take a chance at something comin' in
Everyone will win
